           Alternatively, customer can also pay at the exit lane.            
          </li>
          <li>
          Validators are available to handle special parking concessions.
            
          </li>
          <br />
           The parking systems can be installed at small to large car parks and
          its applications are suitable for hospital, cinemas, hotels, shopping
          mall, office building etc. 
        </Container>
      </div>
